"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561071521","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545913510,"updated_time":1546137810,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e希望那些鼓励梦想的人到时候能负责，在这孩子走错路一无所有的时候能资助。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e反正不管怎么说，我觉得我可能要见证一件大事发生，要么惊天动地，要么哗众取宠。不过，我还是想说一句，那些盲目鼓励题主的人，是不是把科研想得太简单了，当真正接触到这些，哪怕只接触到一点皮毛，你都会感觉自己到自己的力量还是太渺小。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560972479,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1774490fbd6cf33d61cdc8134171d23b","url_token":"nan-hua-83-93","name":"南华","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1774490fbd6cf33d61cdc8134171d23b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560972479","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545903419,"updated_time":1545903419,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果我是菲尔普斯 我能不能进我们大学的游泳队呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560839754,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560839754","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545892440,"updated_time":1545892440,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e孩子，刚学会走路甚至还不稳的时候不要想着能飞到外太空了吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或许你真的对数学有那么一丢丢丢丢的“天分”，但是这点天分完全不足以让你去将哥猜证明出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只希望，你既然能这么心高气傲地有勇气肯定自己的证明，那么在1月1号你的论文发出来被各大神甚至只是普通研究数学的人指出错误的时候，你能有接受网络上所有对你的嘲笑和批判的勇气。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后作为一个也学数学的普通人，我给你的建议是，先脚踏实地好好准备高考。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560786700,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"55c2ccb73ec924eb186c0e1d20673b98","url_token":"okyi-zhi-qiu-zheng","name":"如歌的慢板","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-be997c79772af85676a214128b4ade16_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-be997c79772af85676a214128b4ade16_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"pe