nt":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e高中的时候我们隔壁班有个搞数学竞赛的，一直全省前几名的水平吧，高中刚一入学就说自己证明了哥德巴赫猜想。然后来我们学校有个竞赛大神做数学竞赛培训，隔壁班的大神和大神教练说了自己的证明，说了30min，大神教练说你这不对，就指出了问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我倾向于认为你是伪证，这个东西我觉得初等数论应该不太能解。黎曼猜想你能看懂是什么意思吗？高级数学工具你会吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年轻人证证是好事，但是别太狂了，别变成民科就好。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560193421,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"71b57e2092ee4e17254a6f3e6255ab69","url_token":"ba-zhe-heng-lan-61","name":"霸者横栏","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/71b57e2092ee4e17254a6f3e6255ab69","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560193421","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545816961,"updated_time":1545817179,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你这也太low了吧，才玩到哥德巴赫猜想？我1月1号都要公开用实验证明牛顿第一定律客观存在了  \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560191802,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"83dcf60cabc0c7235e82768c44c55272","url_token":"yan-ting-wei-69","name":"霹雳孙笑川","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/ea56f32f39efbc1249947bd91df4a634_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/ea56f32f39efbc1249947bd91df4a634_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/83dcf60cabc0c7235e82768c44c55272","user_type":"people","headline":"干 ","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560191802","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545816814,"updated_time":1545816814,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你不觉得证明哥猜是以卵击石吗？见到什么都要证明一下，有没有想过中科院的感受？你这简直就是乱猜，说起猜，我就想起了章老师的一句话“戏说不是胡说，哥猜不是乱猜”……明年下半年，中美合拍的《西游记》即将正式开机，章老师将继续扮演美猴王孙悟空，努力创造一个中华英雄形象，弘扬西游文化，文体两开花，希望大家能多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560172241,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"76a4b480552c680db3b67265c2cae058","url_token":"nicholasophie","name":"我道日興隆","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d43a59788f63491f864d3c3853a50502_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d43a59788f63491f864d3c3853a50502_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/76a4b480552c680db3b67265c2cae058","user_type":"people","headline":"正一派道教徒","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560172241","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545815134,"updated_time":1545815134,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e其实题主你可以发到民科吧里，你看看逼乎er们对你的冷嘲热讽，真真是一点也没有学术氛围！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而民科吧不一样，那里学术氛围浓厚，伟大的人民科学家们热烈讨论，理性交流，科学的思维碰撞出一片片智慧的火花。诸多大神藏龙卧虎，各类研究院所掌门人俯仰皆是。相比逼乎而言，那里才有能看懂您大作的大神。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我相信您的大作在民科吧里一定会引起新的高潮！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e祝好！！！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560163116,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"02ed9f71f357d136e44fc847169d3458","url_token":"yi-shen-74-92","name":"义神","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/c1bb6a4abacecb1ff0bbf838ab3a4e08_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/c1bb6a4abacecb1ff0bbf838ab3a4e08_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/02ed9f71f357d136e44fc847169d3458","user_type":"people","headline":"父亲","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560163116","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545814424,"updated_time":1545814424,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀 我在我高三的时候就证明了 当时只给我联系的我当时的导师说了他现在还在验证，不过我早就已经保送了，今年继续陪他验证 刚下飞机就说这些\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560071954,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560071954","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545806774,"updated_time":1545806888,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个答案说会或者不会，其实都可以。说不会，因为这不符合教育部关于保送资格的认定。说会，因为你根本不可能做出来，所以即使基于上一条理由也不能算错。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过可以说的是，这个猜想要是做出来，势必导致一些新的理论创立和新的方法的引入，而且肯定不是抖机灵做出来的，一定是卷帙浩繁的脏活累活，一定足以改变当代人对于数论的认识。凭借这么一套奠基性的工作，只要别像Grothendieck那样到处胡说八道说疯话，估计在世界一流大学找个教授应该没什么问题，混几个数学界耳熟能详的奖励应该也没什么问题。不过我不太相信这是中学生做的事情，历史上还没有这样的先例。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e陈景润论文的理论并不抽象复杂，但是他的分析技巧是极度变态的，这就是他的生存之道。本学渣虽然知道他每一句话是什么意思，但是无法洞察陈景润先生的思路是什么样的，所以并不能很好的理解他的思想。但是目前看来，没有新的理论和观点来重新认识这个问题，几乎没什么做出来的希望。就像费马大定理一样，一个不定方程的整数解，居然用那么多奇奇怪怪不知所云的理论来理解才做的过去。我们不知道什么方法可以，但是我们知道，我们现有的方法不行，一定不行的，我确定。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559947290,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5d58732efe3fb6633b025d38491aff64","url_token":"da-hai-de-nu-xu","name":"大海的女婿","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5d58732efe3fb6633b025d38491aff64","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559947290","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545795813,"updated_time":1545795813,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我记得以前也看过一个问题是大学得了诺贝尔物理学奖能保送研究生吗？现在的孩子真的是，复习压力太大了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559856786,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pi